des:
Join the Resistance! Stop Trump! Now, you can use Alexa to find the next Resistance Event near you.

To use: say "Launch Resist events", then ask to "find the next event near me" or "within 40 miles of Denver, Colorado" or "next event near me after May 15"

Events hosted by https://resistancenearme.org/ but I'm not affiliated with them
